# This project's Vercel deployment is the React (Create React App) frontend
# only. The Python dependencies in requirements.txt belong to the separate
# FastAPI backend (deployed on Render), NOT to Vercel.
#
# Without this exclusion, Vercel auto-detects requirements.txt and runs
# "uv pip install", which was failing on orjson==3.10.6 (a TOML parse error in
# that package's source distribution) and breaking the frontend build.
#
# Excluding it here only changes what Vercel uploads — the file stays in the
# repo for the Render backend.
requirements.txt
